Class Manifest

java.lang.Object
  java.util.jar.Manifest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class Manifest
extends Object
implements Cloneable

The Manifest class is used to obtain attribute information for a JarFile and its entries.

Since:
Android 1.0
